{"tid":2016031,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"理大衝突｜再多12名男女被控參與暴動罪　下周一東區法院提堂","createTime":"2020-05-14T06:00:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-14T09:59:35.000Z","uid":240362,"like":5,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"c3f851df0bb9356a371ed48320c8847b134fd54b","tid":2016031,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T06:00:37.000Z","msg":"去年11月香港理工大學爆發激烈衝突，警方於11月18日清場時拘捕13男2女，年齡介乎16至61歲，當中8男2女其後拒保候查，獲暫時釋放，另外5名男子則繼續保釋候查。警方表示經進一步調查及徵詢法律意見後，今日（14日）在全港各區共拘捕5男2女，連同該5名獲保釋男子，警方暫時共起訴該12名年齡介乎18至60歲的男女一項「參與暴動」罪，其中3人另加控一項「管有工具可作非法用途」罪，1人另加控一項「在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器」罪。案件將於5月18日上午在東區裁判法院提堂。警方指拘捕行動仍在進行中。<br />\n<br />\nSOURCE: 01"},{"pid":"84179f4506e2f1473c485f4f2f3524fc0e859f0b","tid":2016031,"uid":224657,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T06:02:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />手足<br />\n非<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3332b1d44c8a1929a78414bdac8ed2c40063a55b","tid":2016031,"uid":355064,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T06:02:48.000Z","msg":"Condom <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c01de6f0431ab15896f7b7451b9bfe00576c7ab3","tid":2016031,"uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T06:04:06.000Z","msg":"#讀者報料 #已FC讀者身份 <br />\n今朝早有人俾人拍門告暴動<br />\nPoly嗰啲自己ready好<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/easternhawkeye/17078\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Feasternhawkeye%2F17078&d=i3QdlbdnIScuB0pxdHOU7mlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOX